source_functionality: This command invokes the Bash shell, which is a Unix shell and command-line interpreter. It allows users to interact with the operating system by executing commands, running scripts, and managing system resources. The Bash shell provides a command-line interface for interacting with the system, supporting features like file management, process control, and input/output redirection.
